16 Hetuduka, Maggārammaṇattika
Hetuduka, Maggārammaṇattika
24.
68Hetuṃ maggārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu namaggārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . (Sabbattha tīṇi.)
69Hetuṃ maggahetukaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu namaggahetuko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . (Sabbattha tīṇi.)
70Hetuṃ maggādhipatiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu namaggādhipati dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
